Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "ovakvim" in different forms and positions, along with their English translations:

1. *Ovakvim* ponašanjem nećemo postići ništa. (With *such* behavior, we won't achieve anything.)
2. Ne volim *ovakve* stvari. (I don't like *such* things.)
3. On je srećan sa *ovakvim* poslom. (He is happy with *this kind of* job.)
4. *Ovakvim* tempom nikada nećemo stići na vreme. (With *this* pace, we will never arrive on time.)
5. Da li je ikada viđena *ovakva* nesreća? (Has *such* a tragedy ever been seen before?)
6. Molim te, nemoj da me gledaš *ovakvim* očima. (Please don't look at me with *those* eyes.)
7. Naša firma se bavi *ovakvim* projektima. (Our company deals with *such* projects.)
8. Ne sviđa mi se *ovakvo* ponašanje. (I don't like *this kind of* behavior.)
9. *Ovakvom* igrom nećemo pobediti. (With *this* game, we won't win.)
10. Moramo reagovati na *ovakve* situacije brzo i efikasno. (We must react quickly and efficiently to *such* situations.)